			AppTray
			Shows installed applications
			by Dennis Tomas

Brief 
~~~~~ 
AppTray is a panel applet that shows installed applications grouped by category.
Each category is represented by an icon, which brings up a menu of applications 
belonging to this category when clicked.

You need TrayLib 0.3.x and ROX-Lib2 to run it.

TrayLib: ftp://ftp.berlios.de/pub/rox4debian/libs
ROX-Lib2: http://rox.sourceforge.net

